reviewText: Love the movie, but the blu-ray transfer wasn't that great.

it's quite difficult to find this movie (TYTD) on DVD, but when i found it on Blu ray, i was amazed, so i took the High Def version and its incluided the Yards (Mark Wahlber movie, pretty cool to). the image quality is good but not the best, but it still impressive for a low budget movie made for TV.

a great blu ray for the PRICE  !!!!
